### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@origin = http://localhost:3000

###############################################
# AUTH - Better Auth + Ruta custom
###############################################
# Better Auth maneja sesiones via cookies.
# REST Client guarda y envia cookies automaticamente.
# Los POST requieren header Origin (proteccion CSRF).
###############################################

### ========================================
### REGISTRO
### ========================================

### Registrar nuevo usuario
# @name signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-up/email
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "name": "Admin Academia",
  "email": "admin@danceacademy.com",
  "password": "password1234"
}

### Registro con password corto (debe fallar - min 8 chars)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-up/email
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "name": "Bad Pass",
  "email": "bad@example.com",
  "password": "123"
}

### Registro con email duplicado (debe fallar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-up/email
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "name": "Duplicado",
  "email": "admin@danceacademy.com",
  "password": "password1234"
}

### ========================================
### LOGIN
### ========================================

### Login con credenciales correctas
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-in/email
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "email": "asolisaranda.28@gmail.com",
  "password": "Dance2026!"
}

### Login con password incorrecto (debe fallar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-in/email
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "email": "admin@danceacademy.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### Login con email inexistente (debe fallar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-in/email
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "email": "noexiste@example.com",
  "password": "password1234"
}

### ========================================
### SESION
### ========================================

### Obtener sesion actual (Better Auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/get-session

### Obtener info del usuario autenticado (ruta custom protegida)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me

### ========================================
### LOGOUT
### ========================================

### Cerrar sesion
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-out
Origin: {{origin}}

### Verificar sesion invalidada (debe retornar 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me

### ========================================
### CAMBIAR PASSWORD
### ========================================

### Cambiar password (requiere sesion activa)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "currentPassword": "password1234",
  "newPassword": "newpassword5678",
  "revokeOtherSessions": true
}

### ========================================
### ACADEMIAS (Organizaciones de Better Auth)
### ========================================
# En este proyecto, cada "academia" es una Organization
# de Better Auth. Necesitas crear una para poder usar
# los demas modulos (instructores, alumnos, grupos, etc.)
#
# FLUJO:
# 1. Haz sign-up o sign-in (arriba)
# 2. Crea una academia (abajo)
# 3. Copia el ID de la respuesta
# 4. Usa ese ID como @academyId en los demas archivos .http

### Crear una academia (organizacion)
# @name createAcademy
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/organization/create
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "name": "Salsa Mia Dance & Fitness",
  "slug": "salsa-mia-dance-fitness"
}

### Listar mis academias (organizaciones del usuario actual)
# @name listAcademies
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/organization/list

### Obtener academia completa por ID
# Usa el ID que obtuviste al crear la academia
@academyId = REPLACE_WITH_ACADEMY_ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/organization/get-full?organizationId={{academyId}}

### Establecer academia activa
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/organization/set-active
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "organizationId": "{{academyId}}"
}

### ========================================
### INVITAR MIEMBROS A LA ACADEMIA
### ========================================

### Invitar usuario a la academia (como admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/organization/invite-member
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "organizationId": "{{academyId}}",
  "email": "instructor@danceacademy.com",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Invitar usuario como miembro basico
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/organization/invite-member
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "organizationId": "{{academyId}}",
  "email": "recepcion@danceacademy.com",
  "role": "member"
}

### Listar miembros de la academia
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/organization/get-full?organizationId={{academyId}}

### ========================================
### FORGOT PASSWORD (Restablecer contraseña)
### ========================================

### Solicitar restablecimiento de contraseña
### Envía un email con el enlace para resetear
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/forget-password
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "email": "admin@danceacademy.com",
  "redirectTo": "http://localhost:5173/reset-password"
}

### Restablecer contraseña con token
### El token se obtiene del enlace enviado por email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: {{origin}}

{
  "token": "REPLACE_WITH_RESET_TOKEN",
  "newPassword": "nuevaPassword1234"
}
